@GaryMarcus | ❤️ 10 | 🔁 0 | 💬 1 | 👁 895

&quot;Why pay $20/month when the free version is already smarter than I am?&quot;

That's the paradox @GoogleAI hit while designing its AI bundle.

@vikaskansalHQ helped craft Google's AI freemium strategy, which has become arguably the most successful (and profitable) consumer subscription product in history (w/ Gemini, Nano Banana, NotebookLM, Veo3, and terabytes of cloud storage).

In today’s in-depth guest post, Vikas shares all the lessons he and his team have learned about why SaaS freemium playbooks don’t work in AI, and what to do instead.

Inside: why gating your smartest model backfires, the anti-patterns that turn power users into GPU-melting freeloaders, and the three pillars of a modern AI paywall.

